extends indexEmail 

block content 
  p Hello #{firstName},
  p You recently requested to reset your password for your Trekkers account. Click the button below to reset it.
    table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation' border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0')
      tbody
        tr
          td(align='left')
            table(role='presentation' border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0')
              tbody
                tr
                  td
                    a(href=`${url}` target='_blank') Reset Password
    p If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. This password reset is only valid for the next 10 minutes.
    p 
      | Thanks, <br />
      | The Trekkers Team